  "3233940": {
    "name": "Solo Tactics",
    "steam_appid": 3233940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细选择何时切换以及将替换的英雄放置在哪个位置，因为其他两个英雄将处于待机状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有有害的队友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只责怪自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要等待机会—自己创造机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/aadcf612ecff8e172198278228bdec3b.poster.avif?t=1770714310\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/aadcf612ecff8e172198278228bdec3b.webm?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/aadcf612ecff8e172198278228bdec3b.mp4?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高水平的游戏玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过快速切换英雄来执行连招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/4ecce21850a15032de966e9949bf1333.poster.avif?t=1770714310\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/4ecce21850a15032de966e9949bf1333.webm?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/4ecce21850a15032de966e9949bf1333.mp4?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >短暂激烈的战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MOBA格斗游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有金币收集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需等待行动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5分钟一回合（游戏有2回合，一回合为攻击者，一回合为防御者）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直击重点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>攻击者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击者必须至少摧毁一座塔才能攻击目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摧毁塔以生成小兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/ce7e09972b2e51a24b9d4112f35059c4.poster.avif?t=1770714310\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/ce7e09972b2e51a24b9d4112f35059c4.webm?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/ce7e09972b2e51a24b9d4112f35059c4.mp4?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在时间耗尽前摧毁目标，攻击者获胜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>防御者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过将英雄链接到塔上来吸收伤害并保护您的塔，但请小心，当塔受到攻击时英雄将承受更多的伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/eab1efcc89afc69a3b3797b2449f75d6.poster.avif?t=1770714310\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/eab1efcc89afc69a3b3797b2449f75d6.webm?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233940/extras/eab1efcc89afc69a3b3797b2449f75d6.mp4?t=1770714310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间结束时目标仍然存在则防御者获胜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
